title: 820-00165 Air missing Vcore
message: I have a 00165 board without PPVCC_S0_CPU. I removed the inductor L3710 and the CPU-side of the inductors measures 5 Ohms to ground. CPU shorted internally?

title: 820-00165 Air missing Vcore
message:
5 ohm, or 005 in diode mode?
Compare value with good board, with similar CPU.

Any history fault available?

title: 820-00165 Air missing Vcore
message: It's 4-5 Ohms in resistance mode. I checked a good board and it's around 10-20 Ohms.

title: 820-00165 Air missing Vcore
message:
Compare with same CPU type.
i7 has lower value than i5.
